	12 0 M -4 8 L 12 4 M 0 10 L stroke}
>> matrix makepattern
/Pat8 exch def
<< Tile8x8
 /PaintProc {0.5 setlinewidth pop 0 -2 M 12 4 L
	-4 0 M 12 8 L -4 4 M 8 10 L stroke}
>> matrix makepattern
/Pat9 exch def
